# Runtime data directories a `blizzard {hub,runner} init` scaffolds.
data/
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# The compiled Angular apps CI (or a local `npm run build`) embeds into the wheel.
# Nothing here is source: the whole build output — index.html included — is a
# wheel artifact, never tracked, so a clean worktree can never restore a stale
# placeholder over a real build. When no build has run, index.html is simply
# absent and the daemon serves a runtime placeholder (foundation/web.py). The
# wheel still ships these files via pyproject's `artifacts` glob.
/src/blizzard/static/hub/*
/src/blizzard/static/runner/*
